TS Galaxy have announced the details of the late Thembinkosi Mbamba's memorial service and funeral. The 23-year-old midfielder passed away in a car accident on Saturday morning. The club has released the following statement regarding memorial service: 'A memorial service will be held for Thembinkosi 'Bashin' Mbamba on Thursday, 30 May 2019. The service will be held at Duduza Multi-Purpose Centre from 12:00 - 17:00. Please join us in celebrating the life of this young Rocket. Funeral service details Date: Saturday,1 June 2019 Time: 08:00 - 11:30 Venue: Duduza Multi-Purpose Centre The funeral precession will proceed to Nigel Cemetery where Thembinkosi will be laid to rest.